00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:31,600
But we can also have somebody standing in your way physically.
但也可以指有人从物理上挡你的路。

183
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:35,560
Like really you're standing close to me and I can't pass through the door.
比如你真的站得很近，我无法通过门。

184
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,080
Right.
对。

185
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:39,280
So maybe the person is at the door and it's standing in my way.
所以可能那个人站在门口，挡住了我的路。

186
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,160
I can't go in.
我进不去。

187
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:40,640
Yeah.
是的。

188
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,120
OK.
好的。

189
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:44,600
But here we're not really talking about a real thing, right.
但这里我们说的不是真实的东西，对吧。

190
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,720
That you can touch.
你可以触摸到的东西。

191
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,000
Right.
对。

192
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,240
It's more of some obstacle that's preventing you from reaching your goals
它更像是一种阻碍你达成目标的东西。

193
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,760
or from doing what you want to do.
或者阻止你做想做的事。

194
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,240
Yeah.
是的。

195
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,000
So now we can listen to our dialogue again.
那么现在我们可以再听一遍对话。

196
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,840
And now you can understand these words that we've just talked about.
现在你能理解我们刚刚讨论的这些词了。

